external_knowledge:
- "contact details" in this context means email addresses;
- "team affiliations" refers to the department a user belongs to;
- "weather records" accessed in "last year" is defined by the access date being between '2022-01-01' and '2022-12-31'.;
- "status and names of the associated data sources and weather stations" refer to the operational status and titles of the respective entities.

sql:
SELECT AVG(mean_temperature) AS AverageTemperature
FROM weather_data
WHERE est = '2015-01-01';

SELECT data_quality_flag
FROM weather_data
WHERE est = (SELECT MAX(est) FROM weather_data);
